    "content": "IF the user requests that refunds or exchange price adjustments be directed to a different payment method AND the refund/adjustment has already been processed by the system, THEN inform the user that processed refunds cannot be redirected, state which payment method received the refund, and offer available remedies (e.g., issue a separate refund/credit in the requested method if policy permits, provide guidance to contact the payment provider for next steps, or escalate to a human agent for review). If the refund has not yet been executed, confirm the requested payment_method_id explicitly and update the action to use that payment method before calling the action tool.",
